{"data":[{"id":560548601,"type":"answer","answer_type":"normal","question":{"type":"question","id":306537777,"title":"如果高中生能证明哥德巴赫猜想，会被清华北大数学系保送吗？","question_type":"normal","created":1545408745,"updated_time":1545408745,"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/questions/306537777","relationship":{}},"author":{"id":"560aae3c0d11cc3dd4b7c1734c65ac12","url_token":"liu-kai-69-95","name":"羚羊行者","avatar_url":"https://pic1.zhimg.com/v2-c8a63f1ab783091fbdebe44f93af1fe4_is.jpg","avatar_url_template":"https://pic1.zhimg.com/v2-c8a63f1ab783091fbdebe44f93af1fe4_{size}.jpg","is_org":false,"type":"people","url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/people/560aae3c0d11cc3dd4b7c1734c65ac12","user_type":"people","headline":"","badge":[],"gender":1,"is_advertiser":false,"follower_count":107,"is_followed":false,"is_privacy":false},"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/answers/560548601","thumbnail":"","is_collapsed":false,"created_time":1545863087,"updated_time":1545863087,"extras":"","is_copyable":true,"is_normal":true,"voteup_count":8,"comment_count":10,"is_sticky":false,"admin_closed_comment":false,"comment_permission":"all","can_comment":{"reason":"","status":true},"reshipment_settings":"allowed","content":"\u003cp\u003e首先，我的态度跟大多数答主是一样的，\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e但我真的很反感那些莫名嘲讽的人。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e他只是一个高中生，不是民科啊，人家有光明的未来，谁敢说以后他一定证不出来呢？\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e你们就不能善意的引导吗？\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e其实补充一下，\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e我高中的时候刚学数理逻辑那块儿，是充分必要性那一节，当时也是深受徐迟那篇报告文学的毒害，一度幻想自己证明了哥猜，甚至还用了一个晚自习的时间写了好多证明(就是用充分必要性)后来发现自己蠢得可怜。可我到现在也不认为有多么羞耻，最起码我可以用自己刚学的东西去尝试解决一些问题。后来进入大学，越学越觉得自己的无知，正准备着数学系的考研。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e但是有一点我想说明，从题主你的问题来看，证明哥猜能保送清北吗。我跟题主还是有所不同的，我渴望求知，即使将来有一天我的工作不是跟数学有关系的，我也会将数学作为自己的爱好，因为我觉得有趣，我认为数学是最接近神的一门学科(在这里我不是神棍，我只是想说明数学的魅力)。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e所以我建议题主好好学习，考一个好大学，而不是幻想着突然解决一个世界性的数学难题来一飞冲天。这跟幻想自己中彩票差不多，都是意淫。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e脚踏实地，读个phd，领略数学的魅力吧。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003c/p\u003e","editable_content":"","excerpt":"首先，我的态度跟大多数答主是一样的，但我真的很反感那些莫名嘲讽的人。他只是一个高中生，不是民科啊，人家有光明的未来，谁敢说以后他一定证不出来呢？你们就不能善意的引导吗？其实补充一下，我高中的时候刚学数理逻辑那块儿，是充分必要性那一节，当时…","collapsed_by":"nobody","collapse_reason":"","annotation_action":[],"mark_infos":[],"relevant_info":{"is_relevant":false,"relevant_type":"","relevant_text":""},"suggest_edit":{"reason":"","status":false,"tip":"","title":"","unnormal_details":{"status":"","description":"","reason":"","reason_id":0,"note":""},"url":""},"is_labeled":false,"reward_info":{"can_open_reward":false,"is_rewardable":false,"reward_member_count":0,"reward_total_money":0,"tagline":""},"relationship":{"is_author":false,"is_authorized":false,"is_nothelp":false,"is_thanked":false,"voting":0,"upvoted_followees":[]}}],"paging":{"is_end":false,"is_start":false,"next":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/questions/306537777/answers?include=data%5B%2A%5D.is_normal%2Cadmin_closed_comment%2Creward_info%2Cis_collapsed%2Cannotation_action%2Cannotation_detail%2Ccollapse_reason%2Cis_sticky%2Ccollapsed_by%2Csuggest_edit%2Ccomment_count%2Ccan_comment%2Ccontent%2Ceditable_content%2Cvoteup_count%2Creshipment_settings%2Ccomment_permission%2Ccreated_time%2Cupdated_time%2Creview_info%2Crelevant_info%2Cquestion%2Cexcerpt%2Crelationship.is_authorized%2Cis_author%2Cvoting%2Cis_thanked%2Cis_nothelp%2Cis_labeled%3Bdata%5B%2A%5D.mark_infos%5B%2A%5D.url%3Bdata%5B%2A%5D.author.follower_count%2Cbadge%5B%2A%5D.topics\u0026limit=1\u0026offset=918\u0026platform=desktop\u0026sort_by=default","previous":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/questions/306537777/answers?include=data%5B%2A%5D.is_normal%2Cadmin_closed_comment%2Creward_info%2Cis_collapsed%2Cannotation_action%2Cannotation_detail%2Ccollapse_reason%2Cis_sticky%2Ccollapsed_by%2Csuggest_edit%2Ccomment_count%2Ccan_comment%2Ccontent%2Ceditable_content%2Cvoteup_count%2Creshipment_settings%2Ccomment_permission%2Ccreated_time%2Cupdated_time%2Creview_info%2Crelevant_info%2Cquestion%2Cexcerpt%2Crelationship.is_authorized%2Cis_author%2Cvoting%2Cis_thanked%2Cis_nothelp%2Cis_labeled%3Bdata%5B%2A%5D.mark_inf